00:00:08.783 --> 00:00:11.700
Designing a Fighter Jet

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:14.950
As a young boy,

00:00:14.950 --> 00:00:16.950
my friends and I

00:00:16.950 --> 00:00:18.700
walked back home

00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:21.283
from school at Rameswaram.

00:00:21.283 --> 00:00:22.200
On the way,

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.533
we often rested on the banks

00:00:24.533 --> 00:00:27.617
of our village pond.

00:00:27.617 --> 00:00:28.783
While my friends

00:00:28.783 --> 00:00:31.117
practised skimming pebbles

00:00:31.117 --> 00:00:33.783
over the rippling water,

00:00:33.783 --> 00:00:35.117
I would sit and watch

00:00:35.117 --> 00:00:37.950
the cranes and seagulls

00:00:37.950 --> 00:00:42.950
soar in the sky.

00:00:42.950 --> 00:00:45.533
The sight of those birds

00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:47.117
inspired me

00:00:47.117 --> 00:00:49.617
and I dreamt of my future.

00:00:49.617 --> 00:00:52.283
As I grew older,

00:00:52.283 --> 00:00:53.867
my goal became clearer.

00:00:53.867 --> 00:00:56.367
my goal became clearer.

00:00:56.367 --> 00:00:58.533
I knew

00:00:58.533 --> 00:01:01.533
I had to go into engineering

00:01:01.533 --> 00:01:03.367
I had to go into engineering

00:01:03.367 --> 00:01:04.700
to realise my dreams.

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:07.283
The Madras Institute of Technology,

00:01:07.283 --> 00:01:09.367
popularly known as MIT,

00:01:09.367 --> 00:01:10.783
was the best institution for technical studies

00:01:10.783 --> 00:01:14.950
in South India.

00:01:14.950 --> 00:01:17.783
I studied hard to win a scholarship

00:01:17.783 --> 00:01:20.283
that allowed me to study

00:01:20.283 --> 00:01:24.867
in such a well-known college.

00:01:24.867 --> 00:01:27.200
But it wasn’t until the day

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:29.950
I entered MIT that I saw

00:01:29.950 --> 00:01:35.700
my goal standing before me.

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:37.367
The MIT campus boasted of

00:01:37.367 --> 00:01:39.033
two large aircrafts

00:01:39.033 --> 00:01:41.700
that were on display.

00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:43.533
I remember

00:01:43.533 --> 00:01:45.117
sitting near them,

00:01:45.117 --> 00:01:47.117
long after other students

00:01:47.117 --> 00:01:49.367
had gone back to the hostel.

00:01:49.367 --> 00:01:52.783
