to design a fighter jet

00:02:11.700 --> 00:02:12.867
with a team

00:02:12.867 --> 00:02:14.867
of four other classmates.

00:02:14.867 --> 00:02:17.283
of four other classmates.

00:02:17.283 --> 00:02:20.367
