00:02:46.450 --> 00:02:47.950
I’m sure I’ll come up with a better design,”

00:02:47.950 --> 00:02:50.783
I pleaded with him.

00:02:50.783 --> 00:02:53.200
He looked at me

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:54.200
and said,

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:55.367
“Look, young man,

00:02:55.367 --> 00:02:58.450
I’ll give you three days.

00:02:58.450 --> 00:03:00.450
If on Monday morning

00:03:00.450 --> 00:03:02.950
you fail to show me a better design,

00:03:02.950 --> 00:03:04.950
you fail to show me a better design,

00:03:04.950 --> 00:03:06.867
I’m afraid your scholarship

00:03:06.867 --> 00:03:09.117
