“I knew

00:04:08.700 --> 00:04:11.033
I was putting you under stress

00:04:11.033 --> 00:04:13.033
by asking you to meet

00:04:13.033 --> 00:04:15.367
an impossible deadline.

00:04:15.367 --> 00:04:16.200
I never expected you

00:04:16.200 --> 00:04:18.450
to perform so well!”

00:04:18.450 --> 00:04:21.700
to perform so well!”

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:24.700
I had hardly slept or eaten

00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:26.533
in the past three days,

00:04:26.533 --> 00:04:27.700
but I now felt

00:04:27.700 --> 00:04:29.617
a huge sense of joy

00:04:29.617 --> 00:04:31.617
and relief.

00:04:31.617 --> 00:04:34.867
and relief.

00:04:34.867 --> 00:04:37.117
and relief.

