Not only did I keep

00:04:38.950 --> 00:04:40.033
my scholarship,

00:04:40.033 --> 00:04:40.533
I also graduated from MIT

00:04:40.533 --> 00:04:42.867
I also graduated from MIT

00:04:42.867 --> 00:04:44.283
